comments: So, here's the rub: everything under 'original' should not be modified - not the order, not the contents.
It represents all the original sound effects. EUD relies on it. Game data relies on it. Maybe one day we'll
get around to untangling that Gordian Knot, but for now we're leaving well enough alone.
Feel free to add anything to 'scr' - nothing should be order dependent in there. It contains all new sounds
added since the release of SCR.
When looking up a sound by ID, the lookup is not namespaced, which means the ids need to be unique.
